  <!-- Company Boilerplate -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-8">About Galoy</h2>
      <div class="card" style="padding: var(--space-8);">
        <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); line-height: 1.8;">Galoy builds core banking and payments infrastructure that enables traditional and de novo banks to launch products on Bitcoin. The company's technology stack includes Lana (Bitcoin-backed lending platform), Cala (core accounting ledger), and Bria (Bitcoin payments bridge).</p>

        <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); line-height: 1.8;">Galoy is ISO 27001 certified and works with financial institutions globally to bring Bitcoin capabilities to regulated banking. The company offers two implementation paths: the Sidecar Model for existing banks adding Bitcoin alongside their current core, and Primary Core for new Bitcoin-first institutions.</p>

        <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0;">Founded by Bitcoin and fintech industry veterans, Galoy is backed by leading investors including Hivemind Ventures, Valor Equity Partners, and Kingsway Capital.</p>

        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-6); padding-top: var(--space-6); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-default);">
